Package src.main.persistence.controllers

Class PersistenceController

  • java.lang.Object
    • src.main.persistence.controllers.PersistenceController
  • public class PersistenceController
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the persistence controller, it is responsible of downloading and uploading all the files that can be saved.
